data_all <- read_excel(path = filepath, range = "ML34-16450_51-L!A1:EG4090")

# Isolate date from DTS variable and create date variables
data_all$Date <- ""
data_all$DTS  <- as.character(data_all$DTS)
for (i in 1:nrow(data_all)){
  data_all$Date[i] <- strsplit(data_all$DTS[[i]], split = " ")[[1]]
}
data_all$Date  <- ymd(data_all$Date)
data_all$Year  <- year(data_all$Date)
data_all$Month <- month(data_all$Date)

# Divide dataset by each part (50/51)
data_50 <- data_all |>
  filter(PartNumber == "ML34-16450-L")
data_51 <- data_all |>
  filter(PartNumber == "ML34-16451-L")

Ppk Calculation

out_50 <- data.frame(matrix(nrow = 60, ncol = 24))
out_50 <- out_50 |>
  rename("Year"  = X1,
         "Month" = X2,
         "Ppk1"  = X3,  "Ppk2"  = X4,  "Ppk3"  = X5,  "Ppk4"  = X6,  "Ppk5"  = X7,
         "Ppk6"  = X8,  "Ppk7"  = X9,  "Ppk8"  = X10, "Ppk9"  = X11, "Ppk10" = X12,
         "Ppk11" = X13, "Ppk12" = X14, "Ppk13" = X15, "Ppk14" = X16, "Ppk15" = X17,
         "Ppk16" = X18, "Ppk17" = X19, "Ppk18" = X20, "Ppk19" = X21, "Ppk20" = X22,
         "Ppk21" = X23, "Ppk22" = X24,)
out_50$Year  = rep(c(2020, 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024), times = c(12, 12, 12, 12, 12))
out_50$Month = c(1:12, 1:12, 1:12, 1:12, 1:12)

cumulative_ppk <- function(input_data, output_data){
  for (c in 3:ncol(output_data)){
    measure_vector <- c()
    for (r in 1:nrow(output_data)){
      temp <- input_data |>
        filter(input_data$Month == output_data$Month[r],
               input_data$Year  == output_data$Year[r]) |>
        select(4 + 6 * (c - 2))
      measure_vector   <- append(measure_vector, temp)
      output_data[r,c] <- Ppk(unlist(unique(input_data[3 + 6 * (c - 2)]), 
                                     use.names = FALSE), 
                              unlist(unique(input_data[5 + 6 * (c - 2)]), 
                                     use.names = FALSE), 
                              mean(unlist(measure_vector, 
                                          use.names = FALSE)), 
                              sd(unlist(measure_vector, use.names = FALSE)))
    }
  }
  return(output_data)
}

ppk50 <- cumulative_ppk(data_50, out_50)
ppk50$Date <- paste(ppk50$Year, ppk50$Month, sep = "-")
ppk50$Date <- as.yearmon(ppk50$Date)

ppk51 <- cumulative_ppk(data_51, out_50)
ppk51$Date <- paste(ppk51$Year, ppk51$Month, sep = "-")
ppk51$Date <- as.yearmon(ppk51$Date)

Ppk_names <- c("Ppk1",  "Ppk2",  "Ppk3",  "Ppk4",  "Ppk5",
               "Ppk6",  "Ppk7",  "Ppk8",  "Ppk9",  "Ppk10",
               "Ppk11", "Ppk12", "Ppk13", "Ppk14", "Ppk15",
               "Ppk16", "Ppk17", "Ppk18", "Ppk19", "Ppk20",
               "Ppk21", "Ppk22")

Ppk Graphs: ML34-16450-L

for (i in Ppk_names){
  print(ggplot(data = ppk50,
         aes(x = Date,
             y = ppk50[[i]])) +
    geom_line() +
    geom_hline(yintercept = 1.33, color = "red") +
    labs(title = i,
         y     = i))
}
